# ListTitle(title, subTitle, isMain)
- IF: ${exists(title) && length(title) > 0}
    - ```
    ${join(where([MainTitle(title, isMain), SubTitle(subTitle, isMain)], section, exists(section) && length(section) > 0), ',')},
    ${if(isMain, LegendAndColumnHeaders(), '')}
